<item>
            <title>[HBASE-592] Add convenience put method that takes writable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-592</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be very useful to have a put method on HTable that takes a Writable instead of a byte array.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
